=========================================================
  rails_ai_build installed!

  Next steps:

  1. Run migrations:
       rails db:migrate

     If you see DuplicateMigrationVersionError for version 2024 (or similar),
     remove the bad rails_ai_build migration file under db/migrate/ (short
     numeric prefix), re-run: rails generate rails_ai_build:install, then
     rails db:migrate.

  2. Activate (pick one door):

     A) IDE wizard (recommended)
       open http://localhost:3000/rails_ai_build/ui/ide
       → Activate → BYOK / Cloud key / License

     B) Environment keys
       export NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-...   # free: https://build.nvidia.com
       # or OPENAI_API_KEY / ANTHROPIC_API_KEY

     C) Existing install upgrade
       rails generate rails_ai_build:upgrade
       rails db:migrate

  3. Verify:
       rails rails_ai_build:doctor
       # or Doctor tab in the IDE

  4. First win — ask the agent:
       "Add a GET /health endpoint"
       (prefilled in the IDE after Activate)

  5. Engine mount: /rails_ai_build (disable auto_mount to change).

  Docs: docs/SRS.md · docs/FLOWS.md · docs/IDE_UI.md
=========================================================
